The paper discusses the evaluation of search results, which is a core topic in information retrieval (cs.IR). The focus of the paper is on fairness, which is a topic that can be relevant to several sub-categories, including cybersecurity (cs.CY), cryptography (cs.CR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
